<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BALLERMA</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawi lam mia ziete haw hi,
 Puon lopi silhte hi?
 Bangtin a Kumsawt mun nuom hi,
 A hungtun toh theih uh?

[V2]
 2. Gim-leh-dah cheng thuok zo keia,
 Van gam hungtung ahiu;
 Belam No thisana sawp vam,
 Puon lopi a silh ui.

[V3]
 3. En diu, lawpna tum bak chawiin,
 Van Lal chutphah ma ah;
 Hehpih Pa, Pathien na semin,
 Van gam lopi munah.

[V4]
 4. Gilkiel, dangchak thuokta lo in,
 Nisa thuok ta loin;
 Pathien in salhvak zing ta'n a,
 Kumsawt lawpna vakin.

[V5]
 5. Belam No Lalchutphah ma ah,
 A belh Lal lopi chuh;
 Van thildeih tincheng na pie'n tin,
 A mau puipa hina.

[V6]
 6. Van Gam hing diidiei cham chung ah,
 Hinna tui thieng dawn in;
 Ma a thawkna, thasiet mitthi,
 Lalpa'n thiekhul ta'n a.
 7. Pa, Chapa, leh Thagau thiengtho,
 I hozing I Pathien;
 Lopina ma bangin tuhin,
 Kumsawtin kithang hen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>370</hymn_number>
</song>